      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic. At its heart lies the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring independent throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M-Variable differential lock for precise torque distribution. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. While showing minor patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering the visceral feedback and hydraulic steering rack precision that defined the E46 era. A true enthusiast\u2019s specimen ready for the B-roads.",
