      "description": "This vehicle has been exceptionally well-maintained and presents beautifully. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful use such as tiny stone chips on the lower front valance. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the leather seating is supple and free of cracks or tears, and the dashboard remains pristine. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in top form, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. The engine runs quietly and delivers smooth power, while the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. It sits on a set of high-quality tires with ample tread remaining. This is a dependable, turnkey car that offers a premium driving experience without the premium price tag of a brand-new model.",
